# 🔒 Secure Login System

A basic authentication system developed in C++ with protection against repeated failed login attempts.

## Features

- Username and password authentication
- Three login attempts
- Account lock after multiple failures
- Login activity report

## Technologies

- C++
- Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

## How to Compile

```bash
g++ main.cpp -o login-system
```

## Run

```bash
./login-system
```